title: Lana Jewelry Blake Gold Necklace
description:
Delicate gold shapes interlocked in solidarity trickle together to create the ultimate statement piece.  Made of 14-karat gold.  Designed by Chicago designer and founder of the luxe jewelry line Lana Jewelry, Lana Bramlette.  Go glam and channel  your inner celebrity!  

18 with 4 1/2 in. drop
